/// Default rule profile: use each rule's declared severity, disable nothing.
///
/// Selected when `bpmner.rules.profile` is unset or set to `recommended` (the default). New
/// profiles should prefer amending this module over amending the bare schema, so the inheritance
/// chain stays Recommended → custom.
amends "../schema/BpmnRuleProfile.pkl"

id = "recommended"
description = "Use each rule's declared severity. Disable nothing."
